account-profile: Indicates access to Account Login & My Account
caret-left: Navigate to previous item or page
caret-right: Navigate to next item or page. Used with Call to Action
cart: Navigate to shopping cart page. Shows item count when there are items in the cart
chain-link: Created for Get Outside so user can copy the link of a page
check-fill: Indicates success for messages. Use primarily on light backgrounds
check-stroke: Indicates success for messages. Use primarily on dark backgrounds
clock: Indicates backorder item or time of an event or class
external-link: Indicates links that direct to an external site
information-fill: Informational messages. Use primarily on light backgrounds
information-stroke: Informational messages. Use primarily on dark backgrounds
location-pin-fill: Indicates or pins location. Use primarily on light backgrounds
location-pin-stroke: Indicates or pins location. Use primarily on dark backgrounds
minus-lg: Collapses sub-menu or content (good for MD & LG breakpoints)
minus-sm: Collapses sub-menu or content (good for XS & SM breakpoints)
navigation-menu: Opens "hamburger" menu at XS and SM breakpoints
pause-fill: Pause a video. Use primarily on light backgrounds
pause-stroke: Pause a video. Use primarily on dark backgrounds
play-fill: Start playing a video. Use primarily on light backgrounds
play-stroke: Start playing a video. Use primarily on dark backgrounds
plus-fill: Use to add items. Use primarily on light backgrounds
plus-lg: Expands sub-menu or content (good for MD & LG breakpoints)
plus-sm: Expands sub-menu or content (good for XS & SM breakpoints)
plus-stroke: Use to add items. Use primarily on dark backgrounds
question-fill: Help center, help messages, or tip message popup. Use primarily on light backgrounds
question-stroke: Help center, help messages, or tip message popup. Use primarily on dark backgrounds
star-25: Indicates product rating in quarter increments
star-50: Indicates product rating in quarter increments
star-75: Indicates product rating in quarter increments
star-100: Indicates product rating in quarter increments
star-stroke: Indicates product rating in quarter increments
warning-fill: Warning message. Not recommended due to accessibility issues
warning-stroke: Warning message. Not recommended due to accessibility issues
warning-tri: Recommended for warning message. Severity level: medium
x-fill: Recommended for error message. Severity level: high. For more information, see alerts and notifications guidelines
x-sm: Remove items, often used with filter
